### Annotating Playwright Tests

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-api/class-test.md

Demonstrates how to add annotations to Playwright tests, such as linking to an issue tracker. Annotations provide metadata displayed in reports and accessible programmatically.

```js
import { test, expect } from '@playwright/test';

test('basic test', {
  annotation: {
    type: 'issue',
    description: 'https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/issues/23180',
  },
}, async ({ page }) => {
  await page.goto('https://playwright.dev/');
  // ...
});
```

