### Check Request Failure Status (JavaScript, Java, Python, C#)

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/api/class-request.md

Returns details about a request failure if the `requestfailed` event was emitted for this request. Otherwise, returns null. The `errorText` property provides a human-readable error message. Available since v1.8.

```js
/**
 * @returns {object|null}
 */
failure() {}
```

```java
/**
 * @return the failure info or null if this request has not failed.
 */
public String failure() {}
```

```python
def failure(self) -> typing.Optional[str]: ...
    """The method returns `null` unless this request has failed."""
```

```csharp
// The method returns null unless this request has failed.
public string? Failure();
```

